  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manual Samuel is a hilarious, hand-drawn adventure game with a wild twist. After making a deal with Death, our hero, the spoiled rich-kid Samuel, must survive for 24 hours controlling his entire body manually.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From breathing and blinking to driving and working, all these tasks will fall to you. It won’t be easy, with Death himself tagging along for the ride, you might be in some very deep feces!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/504130/extras/4a7566d092c2bc5eb0f0a8d3d93e95e6.webp?t=1747737875\" width=616 height=50 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Overhauled the game to fix a number of gameplay bugs and introduce a number of quality of life improvements</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - Visual updates, revamped character animations, new and improved audio effects, updated controller support</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - Added Simplified and Traditional Chinese subtitles - read feces in up to 12 languages</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 8 new achievements to discover and unlock!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/504130/extras/f7b37f23bcbecb9a4e41139992367761.webp?t=1747737875\" width=616 height=50 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Using your keyboard or controller, you’ll have to manually breathe, blink, drink, walk, talk and more — one clumsy input at a time. Can you keep Samuel alive, or will he flop his way back to the afterlife?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/504130/extras/578cb1f17c52e65b39cdd1be353b1f70.poster.avif?t=1747737875\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/504130/extras/578cb1f17c52e65b39cdd1be353b1f70.webm?t=1747737875\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/504130/extras/578cb1f17c52e65b39cdd1be353b1f70.mp4?t=1747737875\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/504130/extras/5c17e49a79d992430afbeddd17f07d9a.webp?t=1747737875\" width=616 height=50 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From getting dressed, driving to work and (checks notes…) fighting robots? - Help Samuel navigate his day to ensure he returns to his lavish life and girlfriend!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/504130/extras/65c3b9c53158942b2773166f155b0526.poster.avif?t=1747737875\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/504130/extras/65c3b9c53158942b2773166f155b0526.webm?t=1747737875\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/504130/extras/65c3b9c53158942b2773166f155b0526.mp4?t=1747737875\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/504130/extras/4e9f6d6ce0841a61d73996b625b73b4b.webp?t=1747737875\" width=616 height=50 /></span>Looking to lose friends or break up with your significant other? Then this mode is perfect for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/504130/extras/cab21457c4c0c8104d6cc91ec00b23de.poster.avif?t=1747737875\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/504130/extras/cab21457c4c0c8104d6cc91ec00b23de.webm?t=1747737875\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/504130/extras/cab21457c4c0c8104d6cc91ec00b23de.mp4?t=1747737875\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/504130/extras/40e02011beb6d87fdb66854ce2c7d051.webp?t=1747737875\" width=616 height=50 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Unique, hand-drawn 2D art and animation brings the world of Manual Samuel to life in glorious high resolution!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - Five in-game comics exploring the backstory of Manual Samuel's characters</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - Master the brutal 'Speedrun' and 'Challenge' modes across each chapter</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - Scintillating soundtrack by Sondre Jensen and Ozan Drøsdal</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - Over 600 lines of dialogue expertly executed by our eloquent voice actors</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/504130/extras/07d5a56e9e38e2e5df19605c9e3919f7.poster.avif?t=1747737875\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/504130/extras/07d5a56e9e38e2e5df19605c9e3919f7.webm?t=1747737875\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/504130/extras/07d5a56e9e38e2e5df19605c9e3919f7.mp4?t=1747737875\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manual Samuel is a hilarious, hand-drawn adventure game with a wild twist. After making a deal with Death, our hero, the spoiled rich-kid Samuel, must survive for 24 hours controlling his entire body manually.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From breathing and blinking to driving and working, all these tasks will fall to you. It won’t be easy, with Death himself tagging along for the ride, you might be in some very deep feces!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/504130/extras/4a7566d092c2bc5eb0f0a8d3d93e95e6.webp?t=1747737875\" width=616 height=50 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Overhauled the game to fix a number of gameplay bugs and introduce a number of quality of life improvements</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - Visual updates, revamped character animations, new and improved audio effects, updated controller support</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - Added Simplified and Traditional Chinese subtitles - read feces in up to 12 languages</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 8 new achievements to discover and unlock!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/504130/extras/f7b37f23bcbecb9a4e41139992367761.webp?t=1747737875\" width=616 height=50 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Using your keyboard or controller, you’ll have to manually breathe, blink, drink, walk, talk and more — one clumsy input at a time. Can you keep Samuel alive, or will he flop his way back to the afterlife?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/504130/extras/578cb1f17c52e65b39cdd1be353b